Class FXGLAssets

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.almasb.fxgl.asset.FXGLAssets

  • public final class FXGLAssets
extends Object
    Stores internal assets, i.e. provided by FXGL. These can be overridden by "system.properties" file under "/assets/properties/".
